data.description: Seller is motivated, bring an offer to make this your new home! Gorgeous 1900's farm style home will take your breathe away! Recently updated 2 years ago with all new kitchen & bathrooms. Gorgeous floors throughout main floor. One guest bedroom with bathroom on 1st floor with dinning room, living room, & laundry room. Upstairs you walk up to the great bright loft space! Then two guest bedrooms with a bathroom & oversized master bedroom with on suite, his & her closets. Amazing oversized fenced yard for pets & enjoying long summer days in this cute home centrally located to all Historic Sanford has to offer! Home needs new AC & minor TLC. NO HOA & in flood zone X!!! Make this your next place to call home. Sold As- IS
